description: Fighting on the Ultimate Surrender mat this week, DJ takes on Kurt Wild's fresh meat. DJ has shown that he has what it takes to be on top here and he plans on showing his opponent just how to do it. Kurt Wild is soft spoken southern boy with a mean streak. Kurt is well conditioned for the match and looks eager to plant his dick in DJ's face and ass. Can DJ further improve his record or will he get one more loss plowed home by Kurt Wild?
title: DJ vs Kurt Wild
